{"tid":720492,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"沖繩通過釣魚台正名案     日改稱登野城尖閣","createTime":"2018-06-28T03:12:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-28T12:35:03.000Z","uid":184679,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"2f1cbabe09cdb7f43353bb84510f5bb2bfc90a0c","tid":720492,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T03:12:06.000Z","msg":"日本沖繩縣石垣市議會今（27）日通過尖閣諸島（我國稱釣魚台列嶼）「正名」案，將原本登錄的「登野城」名稱改為「登野城尖閣」。市議會表示，在目前的環境下，作為尖閣列島行政管轄的城市，應採取適當措施。<br />\n<br />\n根據《聯合新聞網》報導，2016年時就曾有民眾陳情，希望將沒有「尖閣」字樣的「石垣市字登野城」變更名稱，而石垣市市長中山義隆也表示支持。因釣魚台在日本的行政管轄權屬於沖繩縣石垣市，市長中山義隆認為，若將「尖閣」寫入法律文書中，將會讓國內外更加清楚該島的行政管轄。<br />\n<br />\n不過該案原本力推在去年底前完成，但礙於行政手續延遲交送議會，所以今日才完成變更。市議會還在決議文中聲明，沒有領土問題，在日漸惡劣的環境下，「不採取任何對策的行動仍讓人擔憂，做為尖閣列島行政管轄的城市，採取適當措施至關重要。」<br />\n<br />\n對此，中國外交部新聞發言人耿爽曾表明，釣魚島與其附屬島嶼自古以來就是中國的領土，「中方維護領土主權的決心堅定不移，無論日方玩弄什麼樣的把戲，都改變不了釣魚島屬於中國的事實。」他也對日方更名一事怒斥，目前釣魚台列嶼海域正處於緊張狀態，此行為根本是在製造事端。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E9%80%9A%E9%81%8E%E9%87%A3%E9%AD%9A%E5%8F%B0%E6%AD%A3%E5%90%8D%E6%A1%88-%E6%97%A5%E6%94%B9%E7%A8%B1%E7%99%BB%E9%87%8E%E5%9F%8E%E5%B0%96%E9%96%A3-100506017.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E9%2580%259A%25E9%2581%258E%25E9%2587%25A3%25E9%25AD%259A%25E5%258F%25B0%25E6%25AD%25A3%25E5%2590%258D%25E6%25A1%2588-%25E6%2597%25A5%25E6%2594%25B9%25E7%25A8%25B1%25E7%2599%25BB%25E9%2587%258E%25E5%259F%258E%25E5%25B0%2596%25E9%2596%25A3-100506017.html&d=oF%2B7shHiHnXH04nVPe8eUtr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=6267d7df\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E9%80%9A%E9%81%8E%E9%87%A3%E9%AD%9A%E5%8F%B0%E6%AD%A3%E5%90%8D%E6%A1%88-%E6%97%A5%E6%94%B9%E7%A8%B1%E7%99%BB%E9%87%8E%E5%9F%8E%E5%B0%96%E9%96%A3-100506017.html</a><br />\n<br />\n坐大陸廉航去沖繩尖閣7天團, 既方便, 又快捷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c682fc0bc785fbe57baacc327d9910c3015eda3d","tid":720492,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T03:22:14.000Z","msg":"TVB報導未? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eeb27b109ea6c68eee8a0df2615be07cc4e7597f","tid":720492,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T03:37:57.000Z","msg":"去遊行, 去到盡 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b73daf06b8778f2b2294298bf69df70f5a2f054d","tid":720492,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T11:39:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4159db2efddb8b6d3518dc0d240ecedba0cc54d9","tid":720492,"uid":35790,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T11:50:47.000Z","msg":"「一個日本」，是承認日本完整的領土，包括與中國有主權爭尖閣諸島 ，中國稱為釣魚島。"},{"pid":"cb199ad3e3e90b186dfb5dfb17338a968ccaea96","tid":720492,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T11:51:05.000Z","msg":"廢老廢中：<br />\n<br />\n正呀，去石垣食牛！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屌日本仔又搞事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3aaea158b05cbaec3899c8e4a517e0ab4318c222","tid":720492,"uid":70786,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T12:00:23.000Z","msg":"釣魚台係日本的<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08ad3d11311749936ae37e0f4fe0de9e450391ba","tid":720492,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4159db2efddb8b6d3518dc0d240ecedba0cc54d9","tid":720492,"uid":35790,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T11:50:47.000Z","msg":"「一個日本」，是承認日本完整的領土，包括與中國有主權爭尖閣諸島 ，中國稱為釣魚島。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T12:02:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3651bf3159398d65fa75e0d49176b54ed537ab5","tid":720492,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"08ad3d11311749936ae37e0f4fe0de9e450391ba","tid":72049